{"tid":523424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工作問題唔開心 22歲仔燒炭亡","createTime":"2018-01-08T14:11:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T15:18:42.000Z","uid":154800,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"00557806bd86b641c9e648ba21b30bb0b969d5f9","tid":523424,"uid":154800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T14:11:23.000Z","msg":"青衣長青邨青榕樓，下午5時許，22歲姓余男子被胞姊發現倒卧屋內，旁邊有一盤燒過的炭。救護員趕至將事主送往仁濟醫院搶救，至傍晚6時32分證實死亡。警方未有撿獲遺書，初步調查相信事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。據了解，死者因工作問題不開心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180108/57682849\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180108%2F57682849&d=S5hC4lpB7aC5S1kjtA%2FrcpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=d833f8f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180108%2F57682849&h=ac2ee761\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180108/57682849</a><br />\n<br />\n又一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c371147a88b48e73bc5f36ec38fa738f7fc1c43f","tid":523424,"uid":69886,"like":2,"dislike":36,"score":-34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T14:12:22.000Z","msg":"好野 又死件公屋仔"},{"pid":"7820be08a7aa7bcf9eb620a7a1e3f5017fe6fb5f","tid":523424,"uid":52493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T14:16:01.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"7341bfaaaca78ef3f3c83c345565354a28416e94","tid":523424,"uid":34103,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T14:21:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd3944871899c1956f4e6da38b9068da6f5b497c","tid":523424,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T14:27:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5cc0fcea2bc9f588638542d199ae710714e570fc","tid":523424,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T14:28:30.000Z","msg":"<img sr